DEPENDENCIES
------------
SFML 2.0
g++/gcc	[LINUX]
MinGw	[WINDOWS]

LINUX
-----
run:
	./Compile-Linux.sh

Linux compilation uses dynamic versions of SFML.

WINDOWS
-------
run:
	Compile-Windows.bat

Windows compilation is set to use static versions of SFML
To dynamicly compile remove the following:
	-DSFML_STATIC
	-s from -l*-s
	-static-*
You may need to set the location of SFML in the bat file if MinGw does not know where SFML is.
